\id JUD - Maya-Tektiteko NT -Guatemala 2003 (DBL -2013)
\h Stz'ib'en Juds
\toc1 Te U'j Stz'ib'en Juds
\toc2 Stz'ib'en Juds
\toc3 Juds
\mt1 Te U'j Stz'ib'en Juds
\c 1
\s1 Jun Limb'il
\p 
\v 1 Wetz a'in Juds, q'apo' wib' nkyin'aq'unan te Jesukrist b'ix a'in titz'in te Chaw,\x * \xo 1:1 \xt Mat 13:55; Mak 6:3; Kya 15:13; Gal 1:19\x* wetz nqet ntz'ib'a' ja u'j ntzani te etetz aj uk'lemix b'ix ganimix nim tzan te Qtata Dios b'ix kolomix tzan te Qajaw Jesukrist.
\v 2 Tz'okxwit lo'et tk'u'j Qtata Dios eti'j b'ix qetxwit xhchewsa' ek'u'j b'ix kxqetxwit tgani' nim.
\s1 Ikxjani Titza' Tzan Tel Qniky' Kyi'j Kye Aj Nya'tx Tume'l Nkyexnaq'tzan
\p 
\v 3 Etetz waq erman aj b'an ganimix tzan Qtata Dios, wetz ngan tuq tzan tqet ntz'ib'a' te etetz ti'j te tume'l titza' nqokolet parej qkyaqil. Per ajna'l n'ok wen b'an presis tzan tqet ntz'ib'a' tzan nnimsan ek'u'j ch'in tzan tqet ekolo' tuky'i jun tk'u'jlal te tume'l aj ja' wit'lik jk'u'j, te tume'l aj otzaj q'apo' qetz aj pawamo' te Qtata Dios.
\v 4 Komo ate' junjun xjal oje tz'ox ksamo' kyib' qxol cha la'j-e', a'e' aj atx b'an oqtxi' eb'ajkaj swa' tzan kxik si' tuj il. Kye ja xjal aj k'onti'l Dios tuj kywitzni, te galan aj nk'ulun te Qtata Dios qxol n'oken kyitza' cha tzan kyk'ulun tidi'chq nya'tx galan, b'ix n'el kyik'o' te Qajaw Jesukrist aj a'ox tetz at nim tajwalil ti'j kyaqil.
\v 5 Anke etetz eteb'en kyaqil ntzani, wetz ngan tzan stzaj nna'o' te etetz te ja ntzani: Te Qajaw aj kyetz teq'i' kye qijajil Israel tuj Ejipt, aj kyqet tkolo' kyi'j kye xjal txini,\x * \xo 1:5 \xt Exo 12:51\x* otk'uluj tzan kyponaj kye [qijajil] aj k'onti'l eb'aj'okslan ti'j.\x * \xo 1:5 \xt Núm 14:21-23,29-30; 32:10-13\x*
\v 6 B'ix ax ikxji otk'uluj kyuky'i kye ángel aj k'onti'l eb'ajqet ten tuj kyluwar ja' ojetq kykaj si' sinoke okaj kykola' kyluwar, b'ix astilji te Qtat oje kyekaj tsi' te jun-ele'x tuj jun luwar aj b'an xop max oj tul te jwisy.
\v 7 B'ix ax ikxji oky'ik kyi'j kye aj Sodom b'ix Gomor b'ix kye txq'anky amaq' qaynin tzi aj ja' kye xjal cha nkyek'ajajin tuq b'ix pur xhq'e-e' tuq.\x * \xo 1:7 \xt Gén 19:1-24\x* Astilji owok kyen twitz xhcho'nal tzan kyten iktza' jun yek'b'il kyi'j kye aj owokel kyen twitz te nim q'aq' aj k'onti'l nqextzaj.
\v 8 B'ix anke oje ky'ik kyaqil nini, yatzun kye ja xjal ajna'lni cha nkyeximan, tidi'chq nya'tx galan nkyk'ulu' tuky'i kchi'jel, n'el kyik'o' kyaqil aj at kyajwalil, b'ix nkyeyolin b'an nya'tx galan kyi'j kye [ángel] aj at nim kyajwalil tuj ka'j.
\v 9 Yatzun te Migel, aj ángel aj mas nim tajwalil, tetz aj nq'ojin tuq\x * \xo 1:9 \xt Dan 10:13,21; 12:1; Tmnk 12:7\x* tuky'i te Tajaw Choj ti'j te xhchi'jel Moisés,\x * \xo 1:9 \xt Deu 34:5-6\x* tetz k'onti'l oxik tpoqo', sinoke cha oxik tq'uma' ikxjani: “Qajawxwit xik poqon te yatz.”\x * \xo 1:9 \xt Zac 3:2\x*
\v 10 Per ajna'l kye ja xjal ntzani, kyetz nkyeyolin b'an nya'tx galan ti'j kyaqil tidi'chq aj k'onti'l n'el kyniky' ti'j, b'ix te aj nkyek'ulun k'onti'l nqet kyb'isu' ti'j, iktza' pur txkup-e', b'ix tzan tpaj nini npon kynajsa' kyib'x.
\v 11 Last-alo kyetz, tzan tpaj oje xik kyin aj owok kyen ti'j Kain.\x * \xo 1:11 \xt Gén 4:3-9; Ebr 11:4; 1Wnch 3:12\x* Oje xik kyin junky b'ey tzan kykamb'an jun twi' kyk'u'j iktza'x te nya'tx galan aj oqet tk'ulu' te Balam,\x * \xo 1:11 \xt Núm 22:1-35; Tmnk 2:14\x* b'ix iktza'x te Korey, ax ikxji kyetz okyekamel tzan ktz'akal.\x * \xo 1:11 \xt Núm 16:1-35\x*
\v 12 Oj ewa'an tzan ena'on tkamlen te Qajawil, kyetz ateqet exol per k'onti'l eb'ajil te kyla'jul tuj kyanim.\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Ax: kyetz iktza' “escollos ocultos” aj telponx jun ab'j tuj te nim a' aj b'a'n tzan tpon tnajsa' jun nim bark, ikxji kye aj xjalji tzan tpaj b'a'n tzan kyk'ulun nya'tx galan kxol kye qerman.\f* Nkyewa'an etuky'i'l per k'onti'l Dios tuj kywitz; cha nkyeb'isun ti'j kyk'u'jx; kyetz iktza' muj aj ch'inwt jab' eq'i' titza', cha nxik eq'i' ja'chq tzan kyaq'iq'; kyetz iktza' tze' aj k'onti'l nkyewitzan, oje kyejatz tx'oqo', b'an kamnaqe';
\v 13 kyetz cha iktza' te nim a' aj npununun, nxik xtoloq'in,\x * \xo 1:13 \xt Isa 57:20\x* njaw potx tajsik iktza' te aj n'el kyeq'i' kky'exaw; kyetz naqe che'w aj cha nkyesutin twitz ka'j b'ix cha okyekajel tuj qlolj te jun-ele'x.
\v 14 Te Enok,\x * \xo 1:14 \xt Gén 5:18,21-24\x* aj twuqi' chmanb'aj atx aj taq'len ti'j te Adan, tetz otyolij tyol Qtata Dios kyi'j kyetz ikxjani:
\v 15 “Wetz oxik wen te Qajawil ikja'n tuq stzaj kxol ky'ila'j mil kye aj pawame' a'ox te tetz,\x * \xo 1:15 \xt Mat 25:16-46\x* ikja'n tuq stzaj q'umal ab'l at kypaj kxol kyaqil xjal, b'ix tzan kxik tsi' tuj il kye aj k'onti'l tuq Dios tuj kywitz tzan tpaj kyaqil kyk'ulb'en aj b'an nya'tx galan b'ix tzan tpaj kyaqil aj yol nya'tx galan oxik kyq'uma' ti'j tetz.”
\v 16 Ntons kye aj xjalji cha kyyolinqet nya'tx galan ti'j jun tidi' qa galan qatzun nya'txji, cha kswanqet tpaj junky, cha nkyejoyon tzan kyk'ulun iktza' kyetzx kygan, cha kyyolinqet nim b'an galan kyi'jx, b'ix nkyeyolin galan kyi'j xjal cha tzan kyk'amon jun tidi' galan te kyetz kyuky'i'l.
\p 
\v 17 Per etetz waq erman aj b'an ganimix, instzaj ena'o' te aj oxik kyq'uma' kye tky'ixel te Qajaw Jesukrist etetz,
\v 18 komo oxik kyq'uma' etetz ikxjani: “Aj ch'inky tponb'aj kyaqil twitz tx'o'tx', kye'ul xjal aj xmayiyon-e', b'ix okyek'uluyon tidi'chq aj nya'tx galan iktza'x kyetz kygan.”\x * \xo 1:18 \xt 2Tim 3:1-5; 2Xhp 3:3\x*
\v 19 A'e' kyetz nkyek'ulun tzan kyqet kypawa' kyib' kye qerman, cha nkyek'ulun aj n'el kygani' te kchi'jel, b'ix kyetz k'onti'l Txew Dios tuj kyanim.
\s1 Ntzani Titza' Tzan Qb'et Cha'oj Kyul Kye Aj Xmayiyon-e'
\p 
\v 20 Yatzun etetz waq erman aj ganimix, pe'eten jwert tuky'i Qtata Dios aj ja' wit'lik ek'u'j, pe'exnaq'tzan waq tuky'i Txew Dios,
\v 21 k'on tz'aj naj ti'j etanim titza' te Qtata Dios nkxqet tgani', b'ix pe'etiyon ti'j te Qajaw Jesukrist tzan tpaj n'ok lo'et tk'u'j eti'j b'ix oxe'l tsi' jun etanq'in te jun-ele'x.
\v 22 Intok lo'et ch'in ek'u'j kyi'j kye aj tzunx nna'non ch'in kyanim,
\v 23 b'ix kyi'j kye txq'anky a tgan tzan kykolet etitza' tzan k'on kxik tuj te nim q'aq'. Yatzun kyi'j kye txq'anky, intok lo'et ch'in ek'u'j kyi'j, per intok esi' enab'l, intel etik'o' te nya'tx galan aj nkyk'ulu' tzan k'on tel etin etetz ikxji.\f + \fr 1:23 \ft Ax: intel etik'o' te kyq'anaq aj xhb'akla' tzan te kchi'jel.\f*
\v 24 Ntons te Qtata Dios aj nkxqet tk'ulu' kwent, tetz b'a'n tzan tk'ulun tzan k'on eqet tz'aqik, b'ix tzan exik teq'i' tzan epon twitz tetz aj ja' atqet tuky'i nim xhchqitz'unal, b'ix tzan epon tuky'i'l tuky'i nim chalajsb'il b'ix saq etanim.
\v 25 A'ox tetz te Qtata Dios aj koloyon qi'j tzan tpaj te Qajaw Jesukrist. Intqetxwit jiq'b'a', instenxwit tetz te twitzale' ti'j kyaqil, instenxwit tetz te k'ulul mandad ti'j kyaqil, instenxwit tetz tajwalil mas nim twitz kyaqil. Ikxji atx aj mina' tuq tb'antik te twitz tx'o'tx', b'ix instenxwit ikxji ajna'l b'ix tuj kyaqil tyemp te jun-ele'x. Ikxji kixi'.
